  "detailed_description": "FireSquad is a strategy game about firefighting. <br>You control a group of 4 firefighters whose job is to rescue people from burning buildings.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Control the spread of the fire, make sure it does not reach critical spots,<br></li><li>Clear the way to the entrance so that the firefighters can bring survivors to safety.<br></li><li>Be prepared to adapt your strategy when the fire spreads</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905080/extras/2eb5e8c0f594a23052ac6260bc8ae482.avif?t=1656691233\" width=541 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905080/extras/1fcf7beccff0910de0d05420d28b64ce.poster.avif?t=1656691233\" width=538 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905080/extras/1fcf7beccff0910de0d05420d28b64ce.webm?t=1656691233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905080/extras/1fcf7beccff0910de0d05420d28b64ce.mp4?t=1656691233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Search for survivals in cabinets, beds, and other places where people try to hide from the fire.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905080/extras/a19f18a74b4d966a056cb10f0418fb0d.avif?t=1656691233\" width=541 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905080/extras/b11edae9fb2e7c7aee009b7d10959197.poster.avif?t=1656691233\" width=538 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905080/extras/b11edae9fb2e7c7aee009b7d10959197.webm?t=1656691233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905080/extras/b11edae9fb2e7c7aee009b7d10959197.mp4?t=1656691233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Upgrade your squad between levels to gain leverage.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905080/extras/4d5e9e97682abed84bc6b83c4ecc3b42.avif?t=1656691233\" width=541 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905080/extras/40dd5170fac946306d882a16a2dd2feb.avif?t=1656691233\" width=538 height=388 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You will dynamically increase the difficulty of the game by selecting level modifiers at certain points in the game.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905080/extras/64237e5d3d0f2b22d4b791092027ef93.avif?t=1656691233\" width=541 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905080/extras/ff8da1782ef94110d4e3ea7cb24e64d4.avif?t=1656691233\" width=538 height=388 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast-paced gameplay<br></li><li>Semi-randomized levels to keep the experience fresh each time you play<br></li><li>Three types of buildings with different features<br></li><li>Squad upgrades<br></li><li>Dynamic difficulty selection</li></ul>",
